{
  "stem": "1338.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, of course, the accent on the Jews, obviously, the persecution of those.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we started the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And about not maybe two weeks over towards the end of September, we were already being asked to wear some bands or, as you know, special identifications.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't walk on the main street, the center street, you could only cross it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people were evacuated from their homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And again, mostly the better-offs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were confiscating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My school was immediately-- my school was in a very brand new building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was taken over immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were sent to the girl's school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went with the girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It became co-educational on the 9th of September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I think that something that maybe give you a feeling of what it looked like-- the-- the principal was still the same principal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think the original principal of the-- of the-- of my school was gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I met him, actually, in Israel later on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But he-- this principal of the girl's school was still there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Only very briefly, maybe a week or two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I remember that we had-- it was a class in English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I saw the picture of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Pines right here in this book, which was very strange.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she was standing there in class reading from the English book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A door opened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The principal walked in with two Gestapo officers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he turned to the-- and my teacher looked through the side of her eyes and saw who they were, and continued to speak in perfect German, because she was holding a German class.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he turned to them and says, class in German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They says, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they walked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And immediately, after they walked out, he came back and he says, that's it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
